	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64248336"><p><div class="quote"><p>Python is #1 on both TIOBE's index and the alternative Pypl Popularity of Programming Language index, which InfoWorld says "assesses language popularity based on how often language tutorials are searched on in Google."</p></div><p>
